vote.title: Authorize (1) a twenty-six month cooperative purchasing agreement for program assurances services to support the implementation of the City's new land management system for Department of Information and Technology Services with Gartner, Inc. through the Texas Department of Information Resources cooperative agreement; and (2) an increase in appropriations in the Building Inspection Fund in an amount not to exceed  $2,423,000 - Not to  exceed  $2,548,000 -  Financing: Data Services Fund ($125,000) and Building Inspection Fund ($2,423,000)
